\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Baptist Theological College is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education institution and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. \line The institution has also applied for the accreditation of the a Master\'27s in Divinity. \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
